com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.graphql

Class GraphQLArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.graphql.GraphQLArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphQL

    public abstract class GraphQLArgument
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphQL
    An Abstract base class representing a GraphQL query argument. Individual argument types are accessible via the #of() static factory methods for the relevant argument type, including from a GraphQlVariableDeclaration, and ofEnum(String, String) and ofID(String, String) for the corresponding types
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
